Bermuda Triangle
****************

Technology release 0.0.1

Requirements:
- Linux with glib-2.3 are testet
- gcc with Objective C compiler
- SDL (http://www.libsdl.org)
- SDL_image
- SDL_mixer
- Python 2.3

Installation:
$ cd src
$ make
No system installation yet ;-)

Running:
$ ./bt

What can i do?
You can move the player with the cursor keys. Move the map with the numpad keys. There are still bugs, but hey - it's a T E C H N O L O G Y release. ;-)

Christian Zeller <chrizel@gmx.net>
